@44   = ~Keldorn,

I have given much thought to our marriage, of late, and my heart is troubled. It is imperative that you return to your estate immediately to discuss matters of grave importance. This is a private matter, Keldorn, and does not concern your new friend. I will not detain you long, but I must ask that you return alone. 

